  "plan": {
    "problem": "Inbound ACL R2_IN applied to interface Serial0/1/0 on router2 contains explicit deny entries for OSPF multicast addresses 224.0.0.5 and 224.0.0.6, blocking OSPF Hellos and preventing adjacency formation with R1.",
    "fix_summary": "Remove the two explicit deny entries for 224.0.0.5 and 224.0.0.6 from ACL R2_IN on router2 so OSPF multicast traffic is permitted; risk: this will allow OSPF multicast through the interface and may permit other multicast traffic previously blocked.",
